117
00:07:03,430 --> 00:07:04,890
{\an7}{\pos(247,103)}时间轴   萌

118
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,930
{\an7}{\pos(57,245)}时间轴   Kallen

119
00:07:07,900 --> 00:07:09,310
{\an7}{\pos(61,103)}后期   饿得慌

120
00:07:09,650 --> 00:07:11,100
{\an7}{\pos(253,245)}顾问   老杜

121
00:07:11,270 --> 00:07:12,730
{\an7}{\pos(76,103)}校对   草草

122
00:07:13,570 --> 00:07:15,020
{\an8}{\pos(103.5,246.8)}总监   草草

123
00:08:20,970 --> 00:08:23,970
{\pos(196,180)}纸牌屋

124
00:08:20,970 --> 00:08:23,970
{\an2}{\pos(208.1,242.25)}第五季  第一集

125
00:08:32,900 --> 00:08:42,900
{\an1}{\pos(115.2,227.25)}对马斯特森的搜寻仍在继续
国内恐怖分子在逃

126
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:36,060
据称的恐怖分子扎克瑞·霍松被联调局击毙
Alleged terrorist Zachary Hawthorne was killed by the FBI,

127
00:08:36,060 --> 00:08:39,030
但约书亚·马斯特森仍在逃
but Joshua Masterson is still at large.

128
00:08:39,030 --> 00:08:40,360
米勒一家哀悼之时
While the Miller family mourns,

129
00:08:40,370 --> 00:08:42,340
对逃跑的恐怖分子的搜寻仍在继续
the hunt for the missing terrorist continues

130
00:08:42,340 --> 00:08:44,630
气氛十分紧张
and tensions are running high.

131
00:08:44,640 --> 00:08:46,430
总统虽然提出战争
The president may be asking for war,

132
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:50,550
但看来他已经遭遇了战争
but it seems war's already been declared on him.

133
00:08:46,530 --> 00:08:50,120
{\an1}{\pos(115.2,227.25)}总统肖像被焚烧
中东对总统做出反应

134
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:53,290
{\an1}{\pos(115.2,227.25)}爆发反安德伍德抗议
中东对总统做出反应

135
00:09:03,210 --> 00:09:04,710
我的粉丝
My fans.

136
00:09:05,670 --> 00:09:08,190
联调局正在调查查塔努加市的一起连环枪击案
FBI is looking into a multiple shooting in Chattanooga.

137
00:09:08,190 --> 00:09:11,380
-据报称是与黑帮有关  -不行
- Reports have it gang related. - No.

138
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:16,440
西弗吉尼亚州一架私人飞机坠毁  机械故障
A private plane went down in West Virginia. Mechanical failure.

139
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:18,760
佐治亚州多处房屋失火
A series of homes were set on fire in Georgia,

140
00:09:18,770 --> 00:09:20,450
很可能是纵火
most likely arson.

141
00:09:21,370 --> 00:09:22,930
北卡罗来纳州一家便利店
Convenience store in North Carolina

142
00:09:22,930 --> 00:09:25,350
今晨4点左右爆炸
exploded at about 4:00 in the morning.

143
00:09:25,350 --> 00:09:28,450
-商店在哪  -罗利郊外
- Where's the store? - Uh, suburb outside of Raleigh.

144
00:09:28,450 --> 00:09:30,720
起因仍在调查
The cause is still under investigation.

145
00:09:31,380 --> 00:09:33,740
-我去露个脸  -是  夫人
- I'll make an appearance. - Yes, ma'am.

146
00:09:33,980 --> 00:09:36,760
加在日程里  让媒体有时间出动
Just put it on the schedule so the media has time to mobilize.

147
00:09:36,770 --> 00:09:37,620
是  夫人
Yes, ma'am.

148
00:09:57,450 --> 00:10:00,600
总统对约书亚·马斯特森宣战了吧
I take it the president has declared war on Joshua Masterson.

149
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:02,720
他就不该不让我继续参加通话
He never should've kicked me off that call.

150
00:10:04,030 --> 00:10:06,260
但今天早晨的重点不是政治
But this morning isn't about politics.

151
00:10:07,110 --> 00:10:07,900
是啊
That's right.

152
00:10:07,900 --> 00:10:10,490
我们得对生者表示同情
We need to show some compassion for the living.

153
00:10:10,990 --> 00:10:13,110
对死者表示尊重
And respect for the dead.

154
00:10:19,220 --> 00:10:20,910
他们一家答应了短暂见面
The family's agreed to a moment.

155
00:10:20,910 --> 00:10:24,130
没有媒体  不做讲话  但我们应该能做点什么
No press, no speeches, but we should be able to pull something.

156
00:10:27,820 --> 00:10:29,360
-总统先生  -州长
- Mr. President. - Governor.

157
00:10:33,420 --> 00:10:35,780
他们不知道我们已经为他们做了什么吗
Do they not realize what we've done for them already?

158
00:10:35,780 --> 00:10:37,700
这我说了  先生  但是
I pointed that out, sir, but...

159
00:10:37,700 --> 00:10:40,260
他们家的女儿服了药  目前很脆弱
the daughter's medicated and very fragile at the moment.

160
00:10:40,270 --> 00:10:41,080
好吧
All right.

161
00:10:42,910 --> 00:10:44,230
米勒太太
Mrs. Miller.

162
00:10:45,740 --> 00:10:48,830
-我非常遗憾  -谢谢
- I'm so very sorry. - Thank you.

163
00:10:49,430 --> 00:10:50,930
我保证
And I promise you,

164
00:10:50,930 --> 00:10:52,030
我绝不会罢休
I will not stop

165
00:10:52,030 --> 00:10:55,260
除非所有导致了这场惨剧的人
until everyone responsible for this terrible tragedy

166
00:10:55,270 --> 00:10:56,790
都受到裁决
is brought to justice.

167
00:10:58,420 --> 00:11:01,030
我发誓  上帝为证
And I swear to you, as God is my witness...

168
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:05,030
再不会有人伤害你和你的家人了
no one will ever harm you or your family ever again.

169
00:11:05,460 --> 00:11:09,180
举国与你和你女儿同哀  米勒太太
The nation mourns with you and your daughter, Mrs. Miller.

170
00:11:09,500 --> 00:11:13,120
-谢谢  如果你不介意  -当然
- Thank you. If you don't mind... - Of course.

171
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,410
总统先生
Mr. President.

172
00:11:21,410 --> 00:11:22,720
我就来
I'll be right along.

173
00:11:23,690 --> 00:11:25,550
你今天很忙  先生
It's a busy day for you today, sir.

174
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:28,150
今天很悲伤
It's a sad, sad day.

175
00:11:28,550 --> 00:11:31,210
很遗憾结果是这样
It's a shame things didn't turn out differently.

176
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:35,410
是啊  有些事比我们俩重要  威尔
Yes. Well, some things are bigger than the two of us, Will.

177
00:11:40,410 --> 00:11:41,670
我不希望他在场
I don't want him here!

178
00:11:41,670 --> 00:11:44,470
冷静  梅莉莎  求你
